  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates long-term outcome of patients diagnosed as acute myocardial infarction
      and treated with medication, coronary artery bypass surgery and percutaneous coronary
      intervention in Asan medical center, Korea.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study will collect 3000 cases retrospectively and 2000 cases prospectively.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
